{"tid":2346647,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"建百廠奴役維人 未簽約已違諾","createTime":"2020-12-30T11:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T11:49:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf34f7e791b4df85e0b1aa854b4f1dc344637a1","tid":2346647,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:43:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201230/72I25IZZKZA3NEMJ3ORHLQLH6A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201230%2F72I25IZZKZA3NEMJ3ORHLQLH6A%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSC6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=870eec62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201230%2F72I25IZZKZA3NEMJ3ORHLQLH6A%2F&h=b14583f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201230/72I25IZZKZA3NEMJ3ORHLQLH6A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n建百廠奴役維人 未簽約已違諾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cy3w2vVempRTRiMcya6FZkTsD-A=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J42RCUSSSVBGDKFGQSN5TLNM6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fcy3w2vVempRTRiMcya6FZkTsD-A%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ42RCUSSSVBGDKFGQSN5TLNM6E.jpg&h=311d089f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■衞星圖片顯示中共三年來在再教育營內新增過百間工廠。<br />\n<br />\n外媒昨稱中國向歐盟承諾解決勞工問題，雙方才掃除最後分歧。。。。。。。。。。。事件令不少外國政要質疑中國承諾。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：北京讓步開放市場 中歐投資協定拍板  稱願改善人權 法荷有疑慮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅傑斯轟歐盟不公義<br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨人權委員會副主席羅傑斯昨稱：「歐盟是完全不公義。與一個從事種族滅絕、奴役人民的國家做交易，是最幼稚及愚蠢！」他口中的「種族滅絕」所指的就是新疆問題。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，這些工廠當中，有92間的業務包括「進出口」，出口地點包括。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨人權委員會委員裴倫德（Luke Pulford）亦有轉載相關新聞，稱：「有沒有人可以將這些新聞交到默克爾面前？」諷刺德國為首的歐盟漠視中國的新疆問題。日本共同社亦引述消息稱，日本獲得中國政府強制拘禁新疆維吾爾人的證據，曾向美國與英國政府提供情報。<br />\n<br />\nBuzzFeed News"},{"pid":"acbd93a0276fbc1e3766947b8359350dbed2516e","tid":2346647,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:49:36.000Z","msg":"推比外國人睇啦, 係度睇有乜用"}]}